stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: Worker Start
    
    Idle --> ReadingStream: Check Delayed ZSET & XAUTOCLAIM
    ReadingStream --> ProcessingJob: XREADGROUP Returns Message
    
    state ProcessingJob {
        [*] --> RegisterActive: self.active_jobs.add(msg_id)
        RegisterActive --> StartHeartbeat: Background Thread Refreshes job_lease:id (30s)
        StartHeartbeat --> RunHandler: Invoke Job Handler
    }

    ProcessingJob --> AckAndDel: Handler Success
    ProcessingJob --> ScheduleDelayed: Catch Retryable Error
    ProcessingJob --> RouteDLQ: Catch NonRetryableError

    AckAndDel --> Cleanup: XACK & XDEL + Remove Lease
    ScheduleDelayed --> Cleanup: ZADD Delayed ZSET + XACK/XDEL
    RouteDLQ --> Cleanup: XADD DLQ + XACK/XDEL
    
    Cleanup --> Idle: Loop Continues
